[32m│[0m 5').read()}}                                                                 [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Measure response time                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - If delay occurs, command executed successfully                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Use increasing sleep durations to avoid false positives                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### 2. **Out-of-Band (OAST) Detection**                                      [32m│[0m
