[32m│[0m ```                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Use Burp Collaborator, interactsh, or custom server                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Commands trigger DNS/HTTP requests to your server                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Extract data via: `$(command | base64)` in the URL parameter               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### 3. **Error-Based Detection**                                             [32m│[0m
